quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Toto efwe khwaruma Nuh khubandu bebe mbu: “wikanyilisilie abandubo, eshinyasio eshilulu nishishili okhuboolela.”"
  71,2,"Naboola mbu: “ Enywe Abandu baanje! esie endi Omwikanyilisi wenyu wahabulafu.”"
  71,3,"Mulaame Nyasaye, ne Mumurie, ne muloonde amalako keke"
  71,4,"Alabaleshela tsimbi tsienyu, ne alabameta tsinyanga okhula indukho yenyu. Toto indukho ya Nyasaye niyuula yibetsanga yulile. Abaane nimwakhamanyilekhwo"
  71,5,"Naboola mbu : “ Nyasaye wanje, esie anaanjile Abandu banje eshilo nende eshitere"
  71,6,Habula omulaango kwanje shikwabamatela shiosi shiosi tawe halali okhwilukha
  71,7,"Ne toto buli olwebalanjile mbu khonyoole okhubaleshela, baara tsinzala tsiabu mumarwi kabu , nibefunikha tsingubo tsiabu nibekhulumamia nibooma emirwe obutinyu muno"
  71,8,Mana khandi toto nebalanga mubwang’aang’u
  71,9,"Mana khandi nebakhuumila obutinyu, mana khandi nebalaanga mubwifisi"
  71,10,"Nebaboolela mbu: “ sabe eshileshelo Nyasaye wenyu, toto ye ni Omunji wokhuleshela.”"
  71,11,Alabarerera ifula ikwe nilondokhana
  71,12,"Ne alabahelesia Omwandu nende Abana, ne alabahelesia emikunda nende emialo"
  71,13,Muli murie amulahetsanga Nyasaye eshiriibwa
  71,14,Ne toto yabaloonga likhabi khwikhabi
  71,15,Shimulolanga shingala Nyasaye yalonga amakulu saba nikalondokhaane
  71,16,Nakhola omwesi okhubamwo obulafu ne nakhola eliuba okhuba itaa
  71,17,Ne Nyasaye yabamesia khwiloba shinga emimela
  71,18,"Khandi alibakalusiamwo, nekhandi alibarusiamwo mwesi burusia"
  71,19,Ne Nyasaye wabakholela eshialo okhuba shinga omukeka
  71,20,Khomunyoole okhucheendamwo khutsinjila tsimbambalifu
  71,21,"Nuhu naboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto bo baakhayile, nibaloonda khu ulia owulabametelwakhwo shiosi shiosi khumwandu kukwe nende omwana wuwe halali okhusikha"
  71,22,Ne nibakhola ebifwanga ebikhongo
  71,23,"Ne nibaboola mbu: “olalekhakhwo Abanyasaye benyu tawe, nohomba olalekhakhwo\tWada\tnohomba Suwa,nohomba Yaghutsa nohomba Nasra"
  71,24,"Netoto bo bamala okhukosia abaanji, ne olabameta balia abonooni halali obukori"
  71,25,"Okhurulana nende tsimbi tsiabu berwa namatsi, mana nibenjisibwa mumulilo, neshibanyoola ubahabina owulali Nyasaye tawe"
  71,26,"Ne Nuhu naboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, olalekhakhwo khushialo abamenyakhwo yesiyesi mubakhayi tawe"
  71,27,"Toto Ewe nobalekhakhwo , balakosia Abasumba bobo, neshibalebula halali abonooni abakhayi"
  71,28,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi! undeshele esie nende Abebusi banje, nende ulia wenjila munzu yanje Omusuubili, nende abo boosi abasubila abasatsa nende abakhasi. ne olameta abonooni shiosi shiosi tawe halali obukori"